      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">The better Cabernet when the meal is still beef-driven but you want a little more restraint and table flexibility than the biggest Napa style gives. It is a smart bottle for roast lamb, mushroom dishes, and dinners where structure matters but brute force does not.</p>
